<div class="fs-2">
  Share the good, the bad, and definitely the ugly.
</div>

<p>
  For real though, we'd love to hear what you think. Have a feature request?
  A general comment? Suggestion? Something you really don't like? We're all
  ears and actively work to make this app the best space for fathers.
</p>

<%= form_for feedback do |form| %>
  <!-- TODO: compare to the notifications partial -->
  <%= render "shared/form_errors", object: feedback %>

  <div class="mb-2">
    <%= form.text_area :body,
                       class: "form-control form-control-lg",
                       placeholder: Lib::Constants::CREATE_FEEDBACK_EXAMPLES.sample %>
  </div>
  <%= form.submit "Share", class: "btn btn-secondary btn-lg text-uppercase w-100" %>
<% end %>
